title: My 10 Scans - December 2013 (gnv64)
description:

All are in PDF format with OCR, bookmarks & covers:

01. Body's Battles by Bal Phondke
02. It Happened Tomorrow - A collection of 19 select science fiction stories from various Indian languages by Bal Phondke (Ed)
03. Khushwant Singh Jokebook 5 by Khushwant Singh
04. Laughter The Secret of Good Health by S.P.Sharma
05. Nano - The Next Revolution by Mohan Sundara Rajan
06. The Human Machine by R. L. Bijlani S. K. Manchanda
06. The Sales Representative's Handbook by Charles Attwood
07. The Theory of Everything by Stephen Hawking
08. International Year of Chemistry 2011 (Magazine Article)
10. The 50 Apps That Matter (Magazine Article)
